channel.title: No one is able to loginto webclient
channel.description: Okay.. So i have my server completed with a webclient on my website with auto cache downloader working. And i cant log into client also it shows error connecting for others. I was told if you somehow put the client on dropbox others will be able to play "and see you" because everyone would be playing on the same client ip. So my question is.. is this true? and if so how can i put the client in the dropbox? .zip file on dropbox public? Any help appreciated thank you.

item.title: No one is able to loginto webclient
item.dc:creator: @imsuperman05 imsuperman05
item.description:
@imsuperman05 wrote:

You don’t need to put the client in dropbox, if you already have a autocache downloader, if the webclient loads find but cannot login, then you did not portforward correctly or do not have no-ip.
